’Щ@5379b5ea7a2bb8767c8bf187bd3f15d03b83e7c895bacc15e6d80755603f366aЩОTitle: title: bits not
Path: Flags
Content:
``--signed, -s``
: Always treat input number as a signed number.
``--number-bytes, -n {int}``
: The size of unsigned number in bytes, it can be 1, 2, 4, 8, auto.
